### Create a menu item for Bella Napoli Restaurant (userId: 9)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/restaurants/9/menu
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Italian Feast",
  "description": "A complete Italian dining experience with appetizers, main course, and dessert",
  "price": 39.99,
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/italian-feast.jpg",
  "categories": ["italian", "special", "dinner", "family"]
}

### Get all menu items for Bella Napoli
GET http://localhost:3002/restaurants/9/menu

### Get menu items with pagination (page 1, 5 items per page)
GET http://localhost:3002/restaurants/9/menu?page=1&limit=5

### Get menu items filtered by name
GET http://localhost:3002/restaurants/9/menu?name=italian

### Get menu items filtered by tag
GET http://localhost:3002/restaurants/9/menu?tag=dinner

### Get menu items filtered by price range
GET http://localhost:3002/restaurants/9/menu?minPrice=30&maxPrice=50

### Get menu items sorted by name ascending
GET http://localhost:3002/restaurants/9/menu?sortBy=name&sortOrder=ASC

### Get menu items with multiple filters
GET http://localhost:3002/restaurants/9/menu?tag=dinner&minPrice=30&page=1&limit=10

### Get a specific menu item by ID
GET http://localhost:3002/api/restaurants/9/menu/1

### Update a menu item - CORRECT WAY (don't include menuId in the body)
PUT http://localhost:3002/api/restaurants/9/menu/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated: A complete Italian dining experience with premium appetizers, authentic main course, and homemade dessert",
  "price": 42.99,
  "categories": ["italian", "special", "dinner", "family", "premium"]
}

### Delete a menu item
DELETE http://localhost:3002/api/restaurants/9/menu/1
